author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
Ahead of Black Sabbath's last ever live show tomorrow, Judas Priest have recorded a cover of War Pigs. There have been many covers since its original release in 1970 (some of the links are below), but this one is special, not just because of a memorable encounter some years ago. 

For the full Judas Priest cover:  https://youtu.be/IB6jbWoGtlA?si=FU9c-kHslvEZjWbz

Other covers featured:
Ren & The Big Push: https://youtu.be/azAD9KE9HKE?si=9iKAoLdV2VxBqxsB
T Pain @:48.53: https://youtu.be/91ck0vJBygo?si=UavxsiNZBMJKbxZj
YUNGBLUD: https://youtu.be/9aRQ8HgkL4Q?si=Z4X6LpdxjuqEAev-
Rival Sons: https://youtu.be/FfzLO54ETto?si=emC1LfEBh74Jsvrz
uKanDanz: https://youtu.be/8kVYdLjoyPE?si=x6vsUcVRej2GsVo5
Cake: https://youtu.be/NhmvKYbi7iY?si=JQYTVe41KjBYbr7x
Faith No More: https://youtu.be/pQD-u6FfXp0?si=BtDuz_uAME9tHJUC

To see more from JHRA and soon, outtakes from this episode,  join my Patreon here: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

For Cameo messages: https://www.cameo.com/justinhawkins
